## getRotEncSpeed()



Return rotary encoder current speed

@status current Introduced in 2.3.10


#### Parameters

none

#### Return value

* `number` in list: ROTENC_LOWSPEED, ROTENC_MIDSPEED, ROTENC_HIGHSPEED
        return 0 on radio without rotary encoder
